: “Hab. in regno 
<emphasis id="16D35919FF2583D5FBE55E54FBE9F9B7" box="[1057,1145,1588,1612]" italics="true" pageId="152" pageNumber="152">Cabulico</emphasis>
propè 
<emphasis id="16D35919FF2583D5FB075E54FA87F9B7" box="[1219,1303,1588,1612]" italics="true" pageId="152" pageNumber="152">Hydozyl</emphasis>
