</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2418850BFF2583D5FCF85EF5FABBF877" blockId="152.[801,1452,1684,1932]" pageId="152" pageNumber="152">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF2583D5FCF85EF5FCE3F957" box="[828,883,1685,1708]" italics="true" pageId="152" pageNumber="152">Note.</emphasis>
– The species was not mentioned in 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF2583D5FB3F5EF5FA38F957" author="BOISSIER, E." box="[1275,1448,1684,1709]" pageId="152" pageNumber="152" pagination="139 - 409" refId="ref136317" refString="BOISSIER, E. (1867 a). Cruciferae. Fl. Orient. 1: 139 - 409." type="journal article" year="1867">BOISSIER (1867a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF2583D5FCE55ED5FCC6F936" author="BOISSIER, E." box="[801,854,1717,1741]" pageId="152" pageNumber="152" refId="ref136390" refString="BOISSIER, E. (1888). Flora Orientalis. Supplementum. Geneve, Basel, Lyon." type="book" year="1888">1888</bibRefCitation>
) and was not mentioned in treatment of 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF2583D5FA875ED4FA3CF937" box="[1347,1452,1716,1740]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Lepidium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="152" pageNumber="152" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF2583D5FA875ED4FA3CF937" box="[1347,1452,1716,1740]" italics="true" pageId="152" pageNumber="152">Lepidium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for 
<collectingCountry id="5CB0C59BFF2583D5FC8E5EB4FC38F917" box="[842,936,1748,1772]" name="Pakistan" pageId="152" pageNumber="152">Pakistan</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF2583D5FC795EB5FBAAF916" author="JAFRI, S. M. H." box="[957,1082,1749,1773]" pageId="152" pageNumber="152" pagination="55" refId="ref140019" refString="JAFRI, S. M. H. (1973). Brassicaceae. In: NASIR, E. &amp; S. I. ALI (ed.), Fl. W. Pakistan 55." type="book chapter" year="1973">JAFRI, 1973</bibRefCitation>
), 
<emphasis id="16D35919FF2583D5FB895EB4FB49F917" box="[1101,1241,1748,1772]" italics="true" pageId="152" pageNumber="152">Flora Iranica</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF2583D5FB285EB5FA10F917" author="HEDGE, I. C." box="[1260,1408,1748,1773]" pageId="152" pageNumber="152" pagination="33 - 342" refId="ref139580" refString="HEDGE, I. C. (1968). Brassiceae, Lepidieae, Drabeae, Arabideae, Sisymbrieae. In: RECHINGER, K. H. (ed.), Fl. Iranica 57: 33 - 342." type="journal article" year="1968">HEDGE, 1968</bibRefCitation>
), or 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF2583D5FCE55E95FC69F8F6" author="BRASSIBASE" box="[801,1017,1781,1805]" pageId="152" pageNumber="152" refId="ref136702" refString="BRASSIBASE (2019). Universitat Heidelberg [https: // brassibase. cos. uni-heidelberg. de]." type="url" year="2019">BRASSIBASE (2019)</bibRefCitation>
. However, it was treated by 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFF2583D5FAF05E95FC32F8D6" author="THELLUNG, A." pageId="152" pageNumber="152" refId="ref144151" refString="THELLUNG, A. (1906 b). Die Gattung Lepidium (L.) R. Br. Eine monographische Studie. Mitt. Bot. Mus. Univ. Zurich 28." type="journal volume" year="1906">THELLUNG (1906b: 318)</bibRefCitation>
as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF2583D5FB9D5F74FA38F8D7" authority="Boiss." authorityName="Boiss." box="[1113,1448,1812,1836]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Sisymbrium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="152" pageNumber="152" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="griffithianum">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF2583D5FB9D5F74FAF0F8D7" box="[1113,1376,1812,1836]" italics="true" pageId="152" pageNumber="152">Sisymbrium griffithianum</emphasis>
Boiss.
</taxonomicName>
, though no such material of the species was found in any of the Geneva or other major herbaria consulted. Therefore, the identity of 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF2583D5FC5C5F14FBDEF877" box="[920,1102,1908,1932]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Lepidium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="152" pageNumber="152" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="setosum">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF2583D5FC5C5F14FBDEF877" box="[920,1102,1908,1932]" italics="true" pageId="152" pageNumber="152">Lepidium setosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
remains unresolved.
</paragraph>
